Class HarvestResult

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
ArcHarvestResult
public class HarvestResult
extends java.lang.Object
implements UserInTrayResource

The HarvestResult class describes the result of a harvest. It contains and manages the resources.
